---
layout: base.njk
title: Restorative Justice Services
description: Trauma-informed, community-based restorative justice services from Reach For Youth that focus on healing, accountability, and repairing harm.
---

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <h1 id="hero-title" class="hero__title">
        Restorative Justice Services
      </h1>
      <p class="hero__subtitle">
        Alternative paths to justice that build accountability, repair harm, and empower young people.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT IS RESTORATIVE JUSTICE -->
<section class="section section--warm" aria-labelledby="what-title">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="what-title" class="section-title">What Is <span>Restorative Justice?</span></h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="max-width: 820px;">
      Restorative justice is a <strong>trauma-informed, community-based</strong> approach that focuses on <em>healing, accountability,</em> and <em>repairing harm</em>—rather than just punishment.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PUNITIVE VS RESTORATIVE -->
<section class="section" aria-labelledby="compare-title">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="compare-title" class="section-title">Punitive <span>vs. Restorative</span></h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="max-width: 780px;">
      Traditional systems like schools and criminal systems often focus on punishment. Restorative justice focuses on accountability, healing, and repairing harm.
    </p>

    <div class="compare-grid">
      <article class="compare-card compare-card--punitive">
        <h3 class="compare-card__title">Punitive</h3>
        <ul class="compare-card__list">
          <li><strong>What rules have been broken?</strong> Harm outweighs the opportunity to heal.</li>
          <li><strong>Who is to blame?</strong> Justice is achieved through guilt, with no acknowledgment of the victim.</li>
          <li><strong>What consequences should be given?</strong> Accountability equals punishment—with no opportunity for repair or healing.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="compare-card compare-card--restorative">
        <h3 class="compare-card__title">Restorative</h3>
        <ul class="compare-card__list">
          <li><strong>Who or what has been hurt?</strong> People, relationships, and healing outweigh broken rules. Everyone has a voice.</li>
          <li><strong>What are their needs?</strong> Justice is achieved by identifying needs and repairing harm.</li>
          <li><strong>Who should fulfill those needs?</strong> Accountability equals understanding impact—with an opportunity for repair and positive outcomes.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CORE VALUES -->
<section class="section section--warm" aria-labelledby="values-title">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="values-title" class="section-title">Our <span>Core Values</span></h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="max-width: 820px;">
      At the core of restorative practices is the belief that every individual possesses the capacity for transformation, and every community holds the potential for healing.
    </p>

    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-card__number">1</div>
        <h3 class="value-card__title">Harm affects people and relationships</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-card__number">2</div>
        <h3 class="value-card__title">Accountability involves repairing harm</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-card__number">3</div>
        <h3 class="value-card__title">Those affected should have a voice</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-card__number">4</div>
        <h3 class="value-card__title">Healing happens through dialogue</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-card__number">5</div>
        <h3 class="value-card__title">Reintegration is key</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- KEY STAT CALLOUT -->
<section class="stat-callout" aria-labelledby="stat-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stat-callout__number">13-15%</div>
    <div class="stat-callout__label" id="stat-title">Recidivism Rate</div>
    <div class="stat-callout__context">
      Compared to 50%+ for traditional juvenile justice
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROGRAMS GRID -->
<section class="section" aria-labelledby="programs-title">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="programs-title" class="section-title">Our <span>Programs</span></h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Restorative practices range from everyday conversations that build trust to structured processes that repair serious harm. At RFY, we offer a continuum of services tailored to youth, families, schools, and courts.
    </p>

    <div class="programs-grid">
      {% for program in restorativePrograms.items %}
      <article class="program-card">
        <h3 class="program-card__title">{{ program.title }}</h3>
        <p class="program-card__description">
          {{ program.description }}
        </p>
        <ul class="program-card__list">
          {% for item in program.features %}
          <li>{{ item }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- RESTORATIVE + CLINICAL CONNECTION -->
<section class="section section--warm" aria-labelledby="clinical-title">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="clinical-title" class="section-title">Restorative Justice &amp; <span>Clinical Care</span></h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="max-width: 820px;">
      The foundation of clinical work at RFY is strength-based, systemic, and trauma-informed. Restorative justice practices operate from the same philosophy—they are not separate from our clinical work, but another avenue to address conflict, harm, and healing.
    </p>

    <div class="values-grid values-grid--three">
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3 class="value-card__title">Build Empathy</h3>
        <p class="value-card__text">Restorative processes help clients develop empathy and understand the impact of their actions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3 class="value-card__title">Reduce Shame</h3>
        <p class="value-card__text">Dialogue and accountability lower shame and defensiveness, making repair possible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3 class="value-card__title">Repair Relationships</h3>
        <p class="value-card__text">Clients practice accountability, rebuild trust, and process interpersonal trauma together.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="section process" aria-labelledby="process-title">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="process-title" class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Our restorative justice process is designed to be simple, supportive, and effective.
    </p>

    <div class="process__steps">
      <div class="process__step">
        <div class="process__step-number">1</div>
        <h3 class="process__step-title">Referral</h3>
        <p class="process__step-description">Received from court, school, or family</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process__step">
        <div class="process__step-number">2</div>
        <h3 class="process__step-title">Assessment</h3>
        <p class="process__step-description">Assessment and intake meeting</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process__step">
        <div class="process__step-number">3</div>
        <h3 class="process__step-title">Program Participation</h3>
        <p class="process__step-description">Youth participates in the appropriate program</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process__step">
        <div class="process__step-number">4</div>
        <h3 class="process__step-title">Completion</h3>
        <p class="process__step-description">Completion and case closure</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process__step">
        <div class="process__step-number">5</div>
        <h3 class="process__step-title">Follow-Up</h3>
        <p class="process__step-description">Follow-up support as needed</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
